snippet.title: Puzzle & Dragons Story Promotional Video
snippet.description:
Introducing a new Puzzle & Dragons game! Puzzle & Dragons Story!

Perfect for both puzzle beginners and expert players!
Puzzle & Dragons Story comes to Apple Arcade this December!

Web： https://pad.gungho.jp/padarcade/en/


Apple and Apple logo are trademarks of Apple Inc., and Apple Arcade is a service mark of Apple Inc., each 
registered in the U.S. and other countries and regions.
Subscription required. 30-day free trial, terms apply.
Some games may not be available in your area.
